</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[195,1444,705,1274]" box="[243,1251,738,762]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">
<emphasis box="[243,450,738,762]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Published record</emphasis>
. 
<collectingCountry box="[465,526,738,762]" name="Bonaire, Sint Eustatius and Saba" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Saba</collectingCountry>
in general (Shelley 2006); Windward Side (
<bibRefCitation author="Shelley, R. M." box="[1061,1238,738,762]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" pagination="1 - 108" refId="ref6805" refString="Shelley, R. M. 2002 a. A synopsis of the North American centipedes of the order Scolopendromorpha (Chilopoda). Virginia Museum of Natural History Memoir 5: 1 - 108." type="journal article" year="2002">Shelley 2002a</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
